<html>
  <head>
    <title>Request to join Your Group</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Hi <span class="fn">there</span>,
    </p>
    <p>
      <span class="fn">A person</span> has requested membership of
      <span class="group">your group</span>.
      <span class="fn">A person</span> wrote the following message, to 
      explain why you should grant group-membership.
    </p>
    <blockquote>
      <p>
        <strong>From:</strong>
        <code class="email">some.email.address.com</code>
      </p>
      <pre>
        I am awesome
      </pre>
    </blockquote>
    <p>
      To accept or delcine the request go to the 
      <a href="#">Response page</a> in 
      <span class="group">your group</span>.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
